        <mxCell id="live" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=10;verticalAlign=top;align=center;strokeWidth=2;" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:13px&quot;&gt;Gemini Live API&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i style=&quot;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;[External System · Vertex AI us-central1]&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;gemini-live-2.5-flash-native-audio&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Modality: AUDIO only (text via output_transcription, never IMAGE inline)&lt;br&gt;Native barge-in · 30 voices · 24 langs&lt;br&gt;api_version=v1beta1&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;8 Registered Tools (function calling):&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;1. propose_names — 3 name candidates&lt;br&gt;2. set_brand_identity — name/tagline/story/values/tone&lt;br&gt;3. set_palette — 5-color brand palette&lt;br&gt;4. set_fonts — heading + body font pair&lt;br&gt;5. generate_image — logo | hero | instagram&lt;br&gt;6. generate_voiceover — TTS brand narration&lt;br&gt;7. finalize_brand_kit — package ZIP&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Agent fully autonomous:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Canvas state injected per turn via [CANVAS STATE]&lt;br&gt;Watchdog nudges agent if silent &amp;gt;5s after tool call completes" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="370" width="330" x="1108" y="82" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
