        <mxCell id="notes" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#1a1a1a;strokeWidth=2;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=10;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=6;" value="&lt;b&gt;Key Architectural Decisions&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;• Live API: TEXT+AUDIO modality. Images generated via function calling — NEVER inline.&lt;br/&gt;• Single Cloud Run container serves both FastAPI API and React SPA static files.&lt;br/&gt;• Auth: ADC only (vertexai=True). Zero API keys in production.&lt;br/&gt;• Storage: local FS dev / GCS prod, env-driven (USE_GCS). Signed URL delivery.&lt;br/&gt;• Session state: in-memory only. No DB. 15-min TTL per session_id.&lt;br/&gt;• BrandCanvas is source of truth — ElementStatus drives agent decisions via [CANVAS STATE] injection.&lt;br/&gt;• No phase state machine — agent is fully autonomous (canvas state = agent memory).&lt;br/&gt;• gemini-3-pro-image-preview requires global endpoint (not us-central1).&lt;br/&gt;• Dead code: TEXT_MODEL/FALLBACK never called anywhere, phases.py raises NotImplementedError, pregen pipeline removed." vertex="1">
